#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔷 has enough healthy food,"
msgstr "🔷 tenga suficiente comida saludable,"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔷 has the clothes they need,"
msgstr "🔷 tenga la ropa necesaria,"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔷 stays safe from harm,"
msgstr "🔷 esté a salvo de cualquier daño,"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔷has opportunities to go to school, "
msgstr "🔷 tenga la oportunidad de ir a la escuela, "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔷has medical attention when sick"
msgstr "🔷 reciba atención médica cuando esté enferma o enfermo"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔷 contributes to family needs, like doing chores, "
msgstr "🔷 que contribuya a las necesidades de la familia, como hacer el quehacer, "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔷 learns the traditions and values you wish them to have, such as honesty,"
msgstr "🔷 aprenda las tradiciones y valores que deseas que tenga, como la honestidad,"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔷 has opportunities to express themselves,"
msgstr "🔷 tenga oportunidades para expresarse,"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔷 has opportunities to play, and"
msgstr "🔷 tenga oportunidades para jugar, y"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔷 feels loved and supported, no matter what."
msgstr "🔷 sienta amor y apoyo, pase lo que pase."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "As a caregiver, your role is to make sure your {child}:"
