msgid "🚩 CONTENT: @fields.child_nickname might come across harmful content, such as violence, hateful speech, pornography, or wrong information. This could also include content hating women, people with disabilities, or people following harmful beliefs or agendas that oppose what you want to teach your girls and boys. "
